/* Ques 8:-
(Area and perimeter of a circle) Write a program that displays the area and perimeter of a circle that has a radius of 5.5 using the following formula:
perimeter = 2 * radius * p
area = radius * radius * p
*/

public class Eight 
{
    public static void main(String[] args) 
    {
        System.out.println("area of circle is :- " + 5.5 * 5.5 * 3.14159); 
        System.out.println("Perimeter of circle is :- " + 2 * 3.14159 *5.5);
        
    }
}


/* Output:-

area of circle is :- 95.0330975
Perimeter of circle is :- 34.55749

*/
